## рҹ“Ҡ What You Get

### 1. Architecture Diagram
Shows complete flow:
```
HTTP Requests вҶ’ Router вҶ’ Controllers вҶ’ Services вҶ’ Database
                  вҶ“
              Middleware
```

### 2. Request Flow
Detailed path for a single request:
```
GET /users вҶ’ AuthMiddleware вҶ’ LogMiddleware вҶ’ UserController вҶ’ UserService вҶ’ DB
```

### 3. Dependency Graph
Component relationships and dependencies

### 4. Middleware Chain
Sequence of middleware applied to requests

### 5. Service Interactions
How services call each other

### 6. Database Operations
All database queries and operations

## рҹ”§ Configuration

Create `.api-flow-config.json`:

```json
{
  "framework": "nestjs",
  "include": {
    "database": true,
    "middleware": true,
    "services": true
  },
  "output": "./api-flow-docs",
  "exclude": ["node_modules", "dist", ".next"],
  "autoOpenBrowser": true
}
```

