## рҹ”Қ Framework Support

### Express.js
- вң… Routes (`app.get()`, `app.post()`, etc.)
- вң… Middleware
- вң… Controllers (if structured)
- вң… Services (if structured)

### NestJS
- вң… Controllers (`@Controller`)
- вң… Routes (`@Get()`, `@Post()`, etc.)
- вң… Services (`@Injectable`)
- вң… Middleware and Guards
- вң… Dependencies injection

### Next.js
- вң… API Routes (`pages/api`)
- вң… App Router (`app/` directory)
- вң… Server functions
- вң… Middleware

## рҹ“Ҳ Statistics

Each analysis provides:
- Total routes detected
- HTTP methods breakdown (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH)
- Controllers/handlers found
- Services and dependencies
- Middleware count
- Database operations
- Framework detection

